b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":2997,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"Shop Exchange Limits Refreshed!","message":"<div><span style=\\"color: rgb(41, 105, 176);\\"><strong>[Addendum <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1662105600\\"><\/span>]<\/strong><\/span><\/div><div>This notification previously listed certain items that are not available for purchase that have now been removed.<\/div><div><br><\/div><hr><div>We refreshed the exchange limits for items in the Shop on <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1662012000\\"><\/span>! Even if you&#39;ve already reached the exchange limit, you may now exchange for these items again.<br><br><strong>\\u25a0Treasure Trade for Astral Raids<\/strong><br>You can exchange astral shards, which can be obtained by clearing Astral Raids, for a variety of rewards. To access the Treasure Trade for Astral Raids, select the Shop on the home screen, then tap Treasure Trade and check the Astral Raids section.<br><br>Note: For more information about quests where you can obtain astral shards, tap the magnifying glass icon on each Astral Raids quest, and check the Drop Rewards section that displays on the Quest Details screen.<br><br><strong>\\u25a0Treasure Trade for Void Battles<\/strong><br>You can exchange the materials you obtain by defeating Void enemies for various rewards. To access the Treasure Trade for Void Battles, select the Shop on the home screen, then tap Treasure Trade and check the Void Battles section.<br><br>Note: The exchange limits for some rewards do not reset.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1662012000,"prev_article_id":"3313","next_article_id":"3149","image_path":"","update_time":1662108301}}}'